[INCIDENT-PROBLEM-TAG]
- feature_tag: FT-CHECKOUT
- source_doc: 00_agd\examples\en\10_source\product\checkout_core_spec_en.agd
- section_id: CORE-010
- tagged_at: 2026-03-04
[/INCIDENT-PROBLEM-TAG]

[Incident Root Flow by Feature Tag]
- feature_tag: FT-CHECKOUT
- root_trace_chain: FT-CHECKOUT -> INC-001 -> INC-010 -> INC-020 -> INC-030 -> INC-040 -> INC-050 -> INC-060
- execution_flow:
  1) tag affected section in INC-001
  2) write bug situation in INC-010
  3) draft quick RCA in INC-020
  4) choose fix direction in INC-030
  5) handoff concrete AI task in INC-040
  6) summarize AI output in INC-050
  7) close or continue in INC-060
>>>

